Package: TargomoR
Type: Package
Title: An Interface to the Targomo API
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Mason-Thom", email = "chrismasonthom@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package allows R users to exploit the Targomo REST API. Currently it 
    supports the Polygon, Routing and Time services. The MultiGraph service is not supported.
